| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-4607 — Recovery Inhibition (lockbit3)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 2a9ab6a5-7ac2-5713-aa8a-37666f4529e1"
